# a08f3ea6703045ecbbbdeb0ecc17cb6c
#: ../../conversion.rst:621
msgid ""
"There is a `demo .docx file <http://calibre-"
"ebook.com/downloads/demos/demo.docx>`_ that demonstrates the capabilities of"
