" page size and text placement format. Meaning, it is very difficult to "
"determine where one paragraph ends and another begins. |app| will try to "
"unwrap paragraphs using a configurable, :guilabel:`Line Un-Wrapping Factor`."
" This is a scale used to determine the length at which a line should be "
